# Stop-loss disabled 2026-05-21 after backtest showed stops cost the bot
# ~$2,160 in expected value across 3 verifiable polymarket stop-outs (trades
# #2, #6, #19) that would have recovered to wins if held to resolution, vs
# saving only ~$80 across 9 kalshi long-tail stops that would have lost the
# stake anyway. Re-enable after rule-set rebuild lands and is validated.
